enie remained there.  A few months later--as Freddy was still in 10th grade--she sent him a letter saying that the Lord had healed her. 
\par \hich\af35\dbch\af13\loch\f35 However, for some reason, the United States consulate would not give her a visa, although tests showed she was healed. \hich\af35\dbch\af13\loch\f35 
